**🧧 Supported Versions:**
- 1.21.11 *[LTS]*
- 26.1 *[LTS]*
- 26.1.1 & 26.1.2
- 26.2
- 26.3-snapshot-5 *[TS]*

**🔌 Supported ModLoaders:**
- Fabric
- NeoForge

**🪵 Changelog:**
- Client namespace
- Keyboard mapping on 26.3
- Mark ClientKeyEvent#getKey() as a constant from the Keyboard class
- AvoidWrappedLoader#{isFabric, isNeoForge}
- [Documentation] All ModLoader annotations
- [Block Creation API] 'mapColor' version default instead of GRASS
- [Block Creation API] Presets
- [Documentation] Block Creation Presets - exact descriptions
- [Block Creation API] @_offsetType property
- [Block Creation API] @_sound property
- Mark Block Creation API presets as a test idea
- [World API] #fizz([BlockPos])
- [World API] #drop([BlockPos])
- Fluid API
- `Block Creation API` integration with `Fluid API`
- Blocks#create
- [ModLoader] @AutoFluid annotation
- [Fluid API] @_layer property
- [Server Player] Player Update Abilities Event
- Fog API *(+ with Fluid API integration)*
- [ModLoader] @AutoFog annotation
- Identification#is([string] namespace, [string] path)
- [Fluid API] @_gravity property
- [Fluid API] @_swimmable property
- [Documentation] All fluid properties
- [Fluid API] @_unbreathable property
- Identification#hashCode
- Resource overriding
- [Fluid API] #getColor([BlockPos], [BlockData], [FluidState], [int] avgWater)
- [Fluid API] @_model property
- [Documentation] Most fluid methods

